metadata.name: GEN XYZ Das Occult #9091
metadata.description:
A 10k Generative Profile Pic collection
GEN XYZ Das Occult - by culla - @tamccullough

move over cryptopunks
there is a new group on the scene

100% code - not an image composition

A bunch of common palettes
A selection of rare palettes
And a smaller set of ultra rare palettes
However, rarity will be based on what combinations the code produces

The majority of tokens will not have a special trait
However your token might have one or even multiple special traits
But, be aware that only the last special trait added will be listed in the features

Even then, look closely, because not all aspects of the canvas are included in the features. Collectors should still look closely and choose what they like when buying on secondary.

Which team are you on? X or O?

follow culla on twitter for updates. Or maybe __acolyte__

If the non reserved tokens mint out quickly, Access List mints will have 24 hours to mint reserves assigned to those wallets

Thank you for supporting an emerging artist in the generative art space

Access List reserves were given to holders of the following PFP collections created by culla
2x for each Basqunk held
1x for each Inkspunk, TwoFourQunk, V0iD, DeeManz, Punkasso and CR0$$KULL
You would have needed to transfer the above tokens to your mint wallet at the time of the snapshot

share your tokens on social media with #genxyznft
Made with love by culla using p5.js

metadata.name: Postcard from Amsterdam #28
metadata.description:
Hope you are ok.

I've been busy, doing ok. 
Autumn with some nice warmer days 
trees and leaves in colors

cycling / working 
I was on a ferry-boat this late afternoon,
amsterdam-north to the center
and some great clouds. colors and lightning 
when the sun went down

and sketching this week ^___^

playing with letters, calligraphy

had a big pile of words for a conceptual work

in the past, I used the source of a program
also for the visuals-text output on the screen
and now was thinking, using this concept text next, 
to create- (de)construct a 2D/3D world with it.

But man. words are so 'touchy' and triggering sometimes,
so deleted all offensive, negative, mood-triggering, distracting words, heh..
until I had some fine lorum-like shizzle to work with.


also wanted to make like a kind of 
digital (jungle) zen garden  -____-

was playing around in 
my 2D 3D sketch zen space


I wanted to do something with leaves,
that quickly turned into like a flock of birds

then also start using older 3D to 2D calculations
that turned into a kind of rail road - metro stop
then I thought that's a nice stop!


If we would ever encounter aliens
what kind of 'universal' language would we use
or would they use? 

Recently saw something on tv, - at a friends house
like these alien-shows on cable tv;
humans were ignored by this star-trek federation,
because we were 'not ready'.

Well I like to party at this cool planet in terra-omega-apha-yes-apha-whatever, 
with some nice nebula's around.
I have some cool 'earthy' dancin moves,  and can show some funky letters.
but  our 'leaders' messed up, making a big shit of this planet.
 
Now we are all universal outcasts.. 
lol. sos from earth. please help us keeping-make this 'a great universal paradise'! We have lovely nature, art, great music and dancing!


want to do something with travelling and animation
some crazy and fun movie ideas

I love to focus on
-and see the great 
and wonderful things in life as well

discover new 'blind spots'


want to wish you a wonderful week 

make friends with yourself
and be easy 
on yourself today
ok?

let the past go and flow

a shower to wake up
fresh clothing

create something
work that flow
make it funky again

move like an animal 
that knows kung-fu

xxx amsterdam chillout  0__.  ^__^ 

Nov 4, 2022

- vanilla javascript - a 'rgb+a' pixel engine - the work is 1 html file
- 'pure software' 2D - 3D drawing, 100% pixels baby!
- no webgl or shaders used
- Image composition - check; used some old 8x8 pixelfont/data of mine, no images are loaded
- Animated - builds up, cross between animation and still
- Interactive - mouseclick - you can zoom-in out with mouse (touch-phone is still messy somehow)
- s-key saves image, and also the top alpha image
- space - hide-show the top alpha layer-animation
- redraws after some time, because it's like a movie ticket.


thx..
fxhash & crew
friends and fans 
collectors, art-lovers, coders and artist 
you make it rock! keep the vibe alive!

to the kings of the underground
and to all people struggling, 
keep pushing it; turn it into art and dance

metadata.name: Postcard from Amsterdam #15
metadata.description:
Hope you are ok.

I've been busy, doing ok. 
Autumn with some nice warmer days 
trees and leaves in colors

cycling / working 
I was on a ferry-boat this late afternoon,
amsterdam-north to the center
and some great clouds. colors and lightning 
when the sun went down

and sketching this week ^___^

playing with letters, calligraphy

had a big pile of words for a conceptual work

in the past, I used the source of a program
also for the visuals-text output on the screen
and now was thinking, using this concept text next, 
to create- (de)construct a 2D/3D world with it.

But man. words are so 'touchy' and triggering sometimes,
so deleted all offensive, negative, mood-triggering, distracting words, heh..
until I had some fine lorum-like shizzle to work with.


also wanted to make like a kind of 
digital (jungle) zen garden  -____-

was playing around in 
my 2D 3D sketch zen space


I wanted to do something with leaves,
that quickly turned into like a flock of birds

then also start using older 3D to 2D calculations
that turned into a kind of rail road - metro stop
then I thought that's a nice stop!


If we would ever encounter aliens
what kind of 'universal' language would we use
or would they use? 

Recently saw something on tv, - at a friends house
like these alien-shows on cable tv;
humans were ignored by this star-trek federation,
because we were 'not ready'.

Well I like to party at this cool planet in terra-omega-apha-yes-apha-whatever, 
with some nice nebula's around.
I have some cool 'earthy' dancin moves,  and can show some funky letters.
but  our 'leaders' messed up, making a big shit of this planet.
 
Now we are all universal outcasts.. 
lol. sos from earth. please help us keeping-make this 'a great universal paradise'! We have lovely nature, art, great music and dancing!


want to do something with travelling and animation
some crazy and fun movie ideas

I love to focus on
-and see the great 
and wonderful things in life as well

discover new 'blind spots'


want to wish you a wonderful week 

make friends with yourself
and be easy 
on yourself today
ok?

let the past go and flow

a shower to wake up
fresh clothing

create something
work that flow
make it funky again

move like an animal 
that knows kung-fu

xxx amsterdam chillout  0__.  ^__^ 

Nov 4, 2022

- vanilla javascript - a 'rgb+a' pixel engine - the work is 1 html file
- 'pure software' 2D - 3D drawing, 100% pixels baby!
- no webgl or shaders used
- Image composition - check; used some old 8x8 pixelfont/data of mine, no images are loaded
- Animated - builds up, cross between animation and still
- Interactive - mouseclick - you can zoom-in out with mouse (touch-phone is still messy somehow)
- s-key saves image, and also the top alpha image
- space - hide-show the top alpha layer-animation
- redraws after some time, because it's like a movie ticket.


thx..

friends and fans 
collectors, art-lovers, coders and artist 
you make it rock! keep the vibe alive!

to the kings of the underground
and to all people struggling, 
keep pushing it; turn it into art and dance

metadata.name: Different Intersections - Iteration 4 #193
metadata.description:
This is the culmination of a series of iterations

____ - Iteration 1
____ - Iteration 2
____ - Iteration 3

The iterations were released under the pseudonym Extracurricular Activities.

The algorithmic theme of the iterations was extensive usage of boolean operations (intersection and difference) on polygons to derive interesting composite shapes.

In live mode, add &size=<YOUR_PIXEL_SIZE> to change the pixel size of the image for export (Right click to save). For example, &size=4000 will set the width of the image to be 4000 pixels.

metadata.name: Bento Boxes #21
metadata.description:
Everybody needs a bento box in the cryptowinter.
The project calls for an adopted nostalgia of little kids that has been handed bento box by their parents before school a little moment of protected comfort before heading out for an adventure.

  

The first collaboration project of MEK.txt and IceRain in FXHash. A work based on MEK.txts The Bento Boxes and IceRains excellent codes, Bento Boxes aims to be a fun visual and code exploration project on the generative art corridor. Pure code, no libraries.

Bento Boxes deconstructed the visual system on MEK.txt's artwork, titled almost similarly, The Bento Boxes. Rebuilt it from scratch with codes, adding variants of colours and shapes without losing the strong characteristics of the base artwork.

metadata.name: GEN XYZ Das Occult #8983
metadata.description:
A 10k Generative Profile Pic collection
GEN XYZ Das Occult - by culla - @tamccullough

move over cryptopunks
there is a new group on the scene

100% code - not an image composition

A bunch of common palettes
A selection of rare palettes
And a smaller set of ultra rare palettes
However, rarity will be based on what combinations the code produces

The majority of tokens will not have a special trait
However your token might have one or even multiple special traits
But, be aware that only the last special trait added will be listed in the features

Even then, look closely, because not all aspects of the canvas are included in the features. Collectors should still look closely and choose what they like when buying on secondary.

Which team are you on? X or O?

follow culla on twitter for updates. Or maybe __acolyte__

If the non reserved tokens mint out quickly, Access List mints will have 24 hours to mint reserves assigned to those wallets

Thank you for supporting an emerging artist in the generative art space

Access List reserves were given to holders of the following PFP collections created by culla
2x for each Basqunk held
1x for each Inkspunk, TwoFourQunk, V0iD, DeeManz, Punkasso and CR0$$KULL
You would have needed to transfer the above tokens to your mint wallet at the time of the snapshot

share your tokens on social media with #genxyznft
Made with love by culla using p5.js
